Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.94,0:00:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hearts are resolved!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future of everyone is at stake!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(616,554)}We challenge you to a Duel, Dr. Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,558)}Very well. I will be your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.65,0:00:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.93,0:00:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show him your awesome 'Bring it to 'em', Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could you guys do to me anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I will crush you into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking! You will be the one who gets crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you pay right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you and your absurd ambitions!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. So you say you're opposing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! I'll take the three of you on at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Disk, set!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Mode - Photon Change!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Gazer - Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.54,0:02:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am begging you... Kaito, Yuma, Shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.09,0:02:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future is in your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, what scenery do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}awaits us on the other side of this hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, let's climb it together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:02:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too soon for us to turn back now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.06,0:03:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come to combine\N together the power dwelling inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta release my Soul Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running, keep running, until you get there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, once again, keep those challenges coming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.50,0:03:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friends, keep on living in the here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep pressing onward together no matter what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shared Life will be 4000.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of you will each hold 4000 Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have the first draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(458,498)}"Number 69: The Three Heroes Unite\N One Last Duel For The Future!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show it to you. The Dueling of my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I send Garbage Ogre from my hand to the Graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to add one Garbage Lord from my deck to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, by paying 1000 Life, Garbage lord can be special summoned from the hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I special summon 3 Garbage Lords!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear! 3 Garbage Lords!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,523)}Three monsters at once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(637,526)}What are you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(614,517)}No... No I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(643,526)}It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,507)}I overlay my 3 LV 5 Garbage Lords!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use these three Monsters to build the Overlay Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.68,0:05:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From all the Numbers this stands on top of, the strongest of all Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipped with superior armor that will shock the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it absorb the power of the other Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, No. 53!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart-Earth the Counterfeit Deity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster with 100 ATK\NThis is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it happens, my Number is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...immune to your magic cards, traps and monster effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set 2 cards and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! First is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Yuma! There is something strange with the guy's Number.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A 100 ATK monster, that's what it is! I'll just kick it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are my first opponent, Yuma Tsukumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you will be the first who gets wiped out by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here with me are Shark and Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of Astral, I gained those friends here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral, I'll save you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon Goblinbergh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Goblinbergh has been summoned successfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can special summon a LV 4 or lower monster from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.22,0:06:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear! Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.48,0:07:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will overlay my LV 4 Goblinbergh  and Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With these 2 monsters, I build the Overlay Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! No. 39!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of the bond between Astral and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiring Emperor Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Aspiring Emperor Hope appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at this moment I activate the permanent trap Battle Route!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, while I have a monster on my field,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the opponent's monsters in attack position have to conduct battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean 'What does he mean'?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That monster just has 100 ATK.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... why would he activate a card that forces a battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean, that he wants us to attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. So if someone-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah, then he's beyond help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Hope! Attack Heart eartH!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, you are as reckless as Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Sword Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish... I activate the effect of Heart eartH!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this card is attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can equip it with a monster card from my graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I equip Garbage Ogre to Heart eartH.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Heart eartH will gain ATK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the amount of the ATK of the opponent's battling monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!\NSo this is, what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the ATK of this Number is low,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,every time it gets attacked, it still has the higher ATK than the opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:09:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Heart eartH 's ATK is 2600.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that! Fake Burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I detach one overlay unit to negate the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Yuma! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! The quick play magic Double Up Chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card: If the attack of a monster was negated,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can attack once again, with its attack power doubled!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Hope! Attack Heart eartH once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Sword Double Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see! This is {\i1}my{\i0} Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In front of me, your Hope is nothing but garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be ground to dust by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart eartH's effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sending the card equipped to Heart eartH to the graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will not be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, when Heart eartH's equip card is sent to the graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,half of the amount of the ATK-change will be inflicted as damage to the opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I detach one overlay unit to activate Heart eartH's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The amount of damage Heart eartH inflicted to the opponent
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will replenish my life points!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Number...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It also has an ability to recover life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart eartH... it can raise it's ATK and evade destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after being attacked, it replenishes Life Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just... the strongest of the Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual , you're a botcher with dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With these fangs of mine, I will tear you into shreds! Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is from before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? Are you {\i1}afraid{\i0}, Ryouga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I summon Hammer Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in this duel, I can use the power of my partner's cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I send all the overlay units of Hope to the graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overlay units of my Hope are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being fussy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sending the overlay units to the graveyard,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can special summon Xyz-Remora!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this guy is used for an Xyz-summon,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the materials needed for the Xyz-summon are reduced by the number of overlay units sent to the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overlay my two LV 4 Xyz-Remora and Hammer Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I build the Overlay Network with these 2 monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear, No. 32!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea Biting Shark Drake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, your dueling gave me a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.48,0:13:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my hand I activate the equip magic Shield Fin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I equip it to Aspiring Emperor Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, I'll borrow your Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Hope! Attack Heart eartH!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attack does not reach this genius of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Heart eartH's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this card is attacked, I can equip one monster card from the graveyard to this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When equipped with a card by this effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ATK of Heart eartH
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be increased by the original ATK of the opponent's monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this, Ryouga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trash like you has to be melted down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fake Burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Shield Fin's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, until the end of this turn the original ATK of the equipped monster is changed to Zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it can't be destroyed by battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He figured out the weakness of that Heart eartH.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.84,0:14:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the damage we get is only 100!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Hope's original ATK is Zero now, the ATK of Heart eartH didn't increase!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you I could find the thing's weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! Heart eartH can use its ATK-power up only once per turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if the ATK has not been changed, he can not give effect damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar, Shark Drake! Attack Heart eartH!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depth Bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the starving shark detected a faint smell of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this kind of damage won't affect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart eartH's effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sending the equipping card to the graveyard, this card will not be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What should we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just recovered again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s time to dump your hope too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Heart eartH's monster effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once per turn I can detach 1 overlay unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to inflict the halved amount of damage I received to the opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! The judgment of my genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that guy's life recovery can be changed into an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take over your feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's {\i1}my{\i0} turn! Dr. Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, you are so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you'd try to defy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you to hell for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop annoying me! I will definitly beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto - With these hands, I'll do anything to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I summon Photon Crusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! Photon Crusher!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I special summon Photon Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card cannot be normal summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is an Xyz-monster on my side of the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.98,0:17:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can special summon it from my hand in face-up defense position.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I release Photon Crusher and Photon Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness within the shining galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become the light of hope and live as my servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incarnation of light descends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma's bonds with them are becoming one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.80,0:17:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope... Shark Drake... Galaxy-Eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All their ace monsters are lined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot son, come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It... How is this {\i1}fine{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like your body as a Number Hunter is already at its limits, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the joke! This is what has become of Kaito's body for {\i1}your{\i0} sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still are Kaito's dad, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Faker,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for your lies, me and Galaxy have stained ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time to make you pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, I wonder if you really can?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}True, if I use the effect of Shield Fin, I can inflict damage on him for certain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the problem is, how he will use the effect of the overlay units of Heart eartH.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even the damage he gets, can be bounced back on us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We don't stand a chance against him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, I'll borrow your monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:18:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll attack Heart eartH with Aspiring Emperor Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Useless! When this card is attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can equip to it one monster from my graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will equip it with this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garbage Ogre!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the ATK of Heart eartH is 2600!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the Fake Burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, the effect of Shield Fin, which is equipped to Hope, activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ATK of the equipped monster is changed to Zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it can't be destroyed by battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I attack Heart eartH with Shark Drake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's the same all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Shark Drake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.51,0:19:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depth Bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heart eartH's effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sending the equip card to the graveyard, destruction is prevented.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another effect of Heart eartH activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once per turn, I can detach 1 overlay unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to inflict half of the damage I received, in total 1350, as damage to my opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad! Our remaining life is 1200!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this attack connects...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, kneel before me, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one kneeling here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickplay magic, Photon Prevent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card: While there is a Photon Monster on my field,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the player will not receive Effect damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! And Kaito still has the attack with Galaxy-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy has 2450 life remaining,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if the 3000 ATK of Galaxy-Eyes comes through...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Faker, I have followed your orders all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Number Hunter, I kept on hunting innocent souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believed in helping Haruto with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... all this was a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of Haruto and for those many souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are you ready for your repentance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Galaxy-Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Stream of Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? Did they win?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma and them won, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.98,0:21:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally beat Dr. Faker with our own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves him right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.03,0:21:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:21:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Un... unbelievable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why on earth is there a new Number!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.55,0:22:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on ahead, speeding up our throbbing beats
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.02,0:22:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen boys and girls, here's the secret to boys and girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really just so spontaneous, wild as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You might be a handful, but what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be up to no good, but learn for real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go the unpredictable route and shuffle your cards with a goal in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever you feel like you've lost your way, just take a minute to close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.63,0:23:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout "stop!" with all you've got, and there's your boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just stop here, not when we don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.31,0:23:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we get hurt, we can't just hesitate now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just give up, not when our future's a lot brighter than our today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriousness... It'll only make us keep fighting even harder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always get as fascinated as we want, and we'll fight on every day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.83,0:23:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Number of Faker is confronting us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:23:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By uniting our powers, we thought we had beaten it, but
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.36,0:23:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something unbelievable appeared in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.29,0:23:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Why is there a new Number?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Faker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.02,0:24:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, there still is hope in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.33,0:24:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With our power and our bonds, we will absolutely defeat this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.44,0:24:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.19,0:24:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Most Evil, Horrifying Dragon appears!\NFalse Skeletal God Dragon, Heart-eartH Dragon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.21,0:24:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who on earth... are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.80,0:24:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiring Emperor Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.69,0:24:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shark Drake!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.50,0:24:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.33,0:24:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For these three to fight alongside each other is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.71,0:24:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Hope-Drake-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.69,0:24:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they combined together!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.24,0:24:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no they didn't.
